You can simply ask Alexa to control your “robot”. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “pjrobot” app in the app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our “pjrobot” app and change the appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with the "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “pjrobot” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “pjrobot” skill, and you'll be navigated to “pjrobot” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the robot.”
“Alexa, turn off the robot.”
